  "_comment": "Window-overrun policy parity (Eran 2026-07-12): JS resolveAutoOverrunMin/overrunDecision ↔ Py resolve_auto_overrun_min/overrun_decision must agree on every case. Rule: live door always ASKS on any overrun (coordinator popup); automatic paths (batch) may BOOK an overrun up to scheduling.auto_overrun_min minutes under 'arrive' semantics (default 15), beyond that they DEFER to the next window/day; 'finish' semantics never books an automatic overrun.",
